  "texts": [
    "It is easier to believe ChatGPT than to be skeptical.",
    "Fact-checking and web search are too much trouble.",
    "Table 1 summarizes my interpretation of what the students did with large language models (LLMs).",
    "There are also columns for what the students could have done with traditional NLP and web search.",
    "LLMs such as ChatGPT are amazingly good on metaphors, probably better than nonnative speakers of English."
